> CrudModelRender 渲染器

## 基本使用

```tsx | react | #f8f9fa
import { CrudModelRender } from '@yl-d/low-code';

export default () => {
  return (
    <CrudModelRender
      type="table"
      schema=""
    />
  );
};
```

## 注入依赖

```jsx | react | #f8f9fa
import { CrudModelRender } from '@yl-d/low-code';

export default () => {
  return (
    <CrudModelRender
      type="form"
      schema=""
      require={{
        hello: () => {
          console.log('hello');
        },
      }}
    />
  );
};
```
